    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An action platformer in 3D. Elon must collect all the Burgers scattered around this mysterious place to open the passage back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prologue:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A young teenager called Elon. An adventurous soul, always looking for a thrill. He was known among his friends for his daring stunts and fearless attitude. Inexplicably, Elon found himself on a beautiful island, surrounded by lush vegetation, crystal-clear waters and ancient ruins. But what caught his attention most were the hamburgers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Objective:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for the 250 hamburgers scattered around the place to open the Exit Portal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use all of Elon's skills to perform acrobatic jumps, spins, wall jumps and, above all, his ability to glide without getting tired.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Art image (cover, icons and background) for illustrative purposes only.</p>",
